目前位置：國立交通大學機構典藏
學術出版
畢業論文






















標題: 行動無線通訊電波在市區環境中之傳播模式Modeling of Mobile Radio Propagation in Urban Environments
作者: 陳慶光Chen, Ching-Kuang唐震寰Jenn-Hwan Tang電信工程研究所
關鍵字: 無線通訊;傳播模式;radio propagation
公開日期: 1996
摘要: 在本論文中,吾人利用幾何光學,統一繞射理論及電磁波學理來發展市區
或住宅區的電波傳播模式,並利用RTM方法來建立電波經多重建築物繞射之
模式,以處理不同樓高及樓房彼此間距離不同的情形.為驗證吾人所發展之
理論模式,將在交大校園中選擇適當之傳播環境進行電波場強量測,並將理
論值與量測值互相比較,驗證後發現各驗證模式之準確度不錯.
In this paper, geometric optics, uniform theory of diffraction
and theory of wave propagation are employed to develop the radio
propagation model in a urbanor residential area. The method of
ray transmission matrix is incorporated in the model to explore
the situation when the spacing betweeb rows of buildings is
different and the heights of buildings are different.To assuer
the prediction accuracy of the model, several measurementsare
carried out at the Campus of Chiao Tung University in Hsinchu.
URI: http://140.113.39.130/cdrfb3/record/nctu/#NT850436064http://hdl.handle.net/11536/62143
顯示於類別：畢業論文




















